{"tid":1963444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真推 認真做] 關於區諾軒案件","createTime":"2020-04-08T06:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T11:52:42.000Z","uid":345459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7e32e06fbd1e9c4704ba03f2770e022a3299fec5","tid":1963444,"uid":345459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:42:19.000Z","msg":"作為真香港人 除左國際線，籌款支援線等等。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得作為真香港人既我地，今日應該都要做番d野。<br />\n<br />\n我唔理你用寫信好，出電郵好 又或是什麼既途徑 什麼既方法 都需要用排山倒海般既力<br />\n<br />\n將以下一則報導(@文章最底下)活生生呈現係終審法院首席法官 馬道立。<br />\n<br />\n第二個人我唔敢講，唯獨馬道立法官先至比到真香港人一種沒有改變既法治原則，而唔係人治！<br />\n<br />\n希望各位仍心存一團不滅之火既大家<br />\n都出一分力！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">**力陳外判主控官 陳文慧 身為法官，其政治立場與身為法官完全不相符，要求馬官作出適當處理**</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n@ <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8D%80%E8%AB%BE%E8%BB%92%E6%A1%88%E5%A4%96%E5%88%A4%E4%B8%BB%E6%8E%A7%E5%AE%98-%E5%90%8C%E5%90%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%A8%A3-fb-%E5%B8%B3%E6%88%B6%E6%94%BF%E8%A6%8B%E6%B7%B1%E8%97%8D-%E7%BD%B5%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E9%BB%83%E5%B1%8D%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98-%E4%BA%BA%E6%B8%A3%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE/?fbclid=IwAR2a8LjQUM6y0pkLQU0Vd8j7Sz9x4U74NfLuGIyc9itue2Ife0k5dQYAJ9s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E8%25BB%2592%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%2588%25A4%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%25A8%25A3-fb-%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E6%2588%25B6%25E6%2594%25BF%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E8%2597%258D-%25E7%25BD%25B5%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25B1%258D%25E6%259B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B4-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B8%25A3%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2a8LjQUM6y0pkLQU0Vd8j7Sz9x4U74NfLuGIyc9itue2Ife0k5dQYAJ9s&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=3856b9f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thes